OL,5, Andrew Maximov has been working in the 
OL,6, computer games industry for 12 years,  
OL,7, but despite all that experience he     
OL,8, still marvels at the amount of money   
OL,9, spent on building the biggest titles.  
OL,11,F"I used to work for PlayStation and the
OL,12,Flast game that I worked on, just       
OL,13,Fproduction alone cost us $220 (#176m), 
OL,14,Fand then you double that for marketing,
OL,15,Fand you are in half a billion dollars  
OL,16,Ffor every game that you put out there, 
OL,17,Fwhich is a bit unsustainable for most  
OL,18,Fcompanies."                            
